text: José Raúl Mulino Quintero (born 13 June 1959) is a Panamanian lawyer, diplomat and politician who is the 39th President of Panama since 2024. He ran for president in the 2024 general election, replacing former president Ricardo Martinelli as the Realizing Goals nominee. ==Notes== ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Presidents of Panama Category:North American diplomats Category:Panamanian lawyers Category:Current national leaders
